natspec.author: Ocean Protocol Team
natspec.details: Implementation of Ocean DataTokens Factory *      Factory deploys DataToken proxy contracts.     New DataToken proxy contracts are links to the template contract's bytecode.      Proxy contract functionality is based on Ocean Protocol custom implementation of ERC1167 standard.

constructor.details: constructor     Called on contract deployment. Could not be called with zero address parameters.

params._feeManager: refers to the address of a fee manager .
params._template: refers to the address of a deployed DataToken contract.

createToken(string).details: Deploys new DataToken proxy contract.     Template contract address could not be a zero address.
createToken(string).return: address of a new proxy DataToken contract
